{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 16:17:51.930424", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission complete.\n\n- Is anomaly: true\n- Faulty devices: pc_0_0\n- Root cause: host_incorrect_gateway\n\nRationale: pc_0_0 lacks a default route to its leaf gateway (10.0.0.1), causing “Network is unreachable” for off-subnet traffic. Control-plane and the rest of the fabric are healthy; issue is localized to pc_0_0’s L3 configuration.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2003, "output_tokens": 94, "total_tokens": 2097, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1920}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
